==English==

===Noun===
'''[[golden]] [[boy]]'''

# A young [[man]] who has become unusually [[successful]] at an early [[age]].
#:''Bill Gates was the golden boy of operating systems.''
# A favored youth, held in high esteem by others, and for whom there are high hopes.

